00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
Ever seen a doughnut that could change the world?

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:07,600
Introducing the tokamak—a magnetic bottle designed to contain fusion plasma.

3
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:13,200
Fusion is the process that powers the sun, but harnessing it is incredibly challenging.

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:18,800
Tokamaks use powerful magnetic fields to keep plasma stable at extreme temperatures—millions of degrees!

5
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:22,800
If successful, tokamaks could lead to nearly limitless clean energy.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:26,400
